# CMPE492-Design-and-Implementation-of-a-Robust-LLMOps-Platform Development Guidelines

Auto-generated from all feature plans. Last updated: 2026-05-24

## Active Technologies
- Python 3.11 (backend + frontend) + FastAPI 0.135, Pydantic 2.12, huggingface_hub 1.7, Streamlit 1.55, pytest, pytest-asyncio, httpx (006-session-persistence)
- In-memory backend session registry (process-local) + browser cookie-persisted session token for Streamlit client continuity; no database (006-session-persistence)
- SQLite file at `backend/data/llmops.db` (3 tables: `gcp_credentials`, `deployments`, `lightning_ai_credentials`). Credentials encrypted with Fernet; key read from `LLMOPS_ENCRYPTION_KEY` env var. (007-gke-inference-pipeline, 008-gpu-cpu-deploy)
- `lightning-sdk` (Lightning AI Python SDK) for GPU deployment submission, status polling, and teardown via Lightning AI managed cloud. `litserve` for LitServe+vLLM server script generation. (008-gpu-cpu-deploy)
- `HF_TOKEN` injected as a transient env var into every deployment environment (GKE pod + Lightning AI job) at launch time — never persisted in DB, logs, or API responses. (009-local-model-hf-deploy)
- `model_origin` field on `DeploymentRow` (`"uploaded"` | `"public"`) determined at deploy time by comparing the `hf_model_id` owner segment to the authenticated HF username. (009-local-model-hf-deploy)
- Upload size: 10 GB per file (Streamlit `maxUploadSize` in `frontend/.streamlit/config.toml`); backend total limit configurable via `LLMOPS_MAX_UPLOAD_BYTES` env var, defaulting to 50 GB (set to 0 to disable). (009-local-model-hf-deploy)
- SQLite at `backend/data/llmops.db` — `deployment_monitoring` table tracks scrape job name, Grafana datasource/dashboard UIDs, provision status, and decommission schedule. Time-series data lives in Prometheus (30d retention). (010-prometheus-grafana-monitoring)
- `prometheus-client` for proxy metrics at `GET /metrics`; Prometheus + Grafana via `docker-compose.monitoring.yml`. HMAC-signed Grafana deep links (`LLMOPS_GRAFANA_SIGNING_SECRET`). Set `LLMOPS_METRICS_DISABLED=1` in tests. (010-prometheus-grafana-monitoring)

